l, City Clerk of [[Berwyn, Illinois]]\n* [[Tari Renner]], Mayor of [[Bloomington, Illinois]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Renner 'wholeheartedly' endorses State Sen. Biss for governor|url=http://www.pantagraph.com/news/local/government-and-politics/elections/renner-endorses-state-sen-biss-for-governor/article_c8d65c3f-d73f-5cdf-a292-a83849da4cf4.html|website=Pantagraph|accessdate=26 July 2017}}</ref>\n* Carlo Robustelli, [[McLean County, IL#Government|McLean County]] Board Member<ref>{{cite tweet|user=carlorobustelli|number=967205633689710592|title=I agree wholeheartedly with The Pantagraph that Daniel Biss is the best choice for Governor.|date=February 23, 2018}}</ref>\n* Alderman Robin Rue Simmons of Evanston's 5th ward<ref name=\"Who's on Team Biss\"/>\n* Debra Shore, [[Metropolitan Water Reclamation District of Greater Chicago]] commissioner<ref>{{cite video|url=https://www.facebook.com/DebraShoreMWRD/videos/1660368683974700/|title=I am proud to celebrate the anniversary of women's suffrage by supporting a champion for issues important to women and families! #WomenForBiss|date=August 26, 2017|accessdate=November 28, 2017}}</ref>\n* Jose Villalobos, [[Elgin Township, Kane County, Illinois|Elgin Township]] Trustee and founder of Progressives of Kane County<ref>{{cite tweet|user=JoseAVillalobos|author=Jose A. Villalobos|number=967404767436791808|title=This is what the future of Illinois should look like. #TeamBiss|date=February 24, 2018}}</ref>\n\n;Organizations\n* 45th Ward Independent Democrats<ref name=\"danielbiss.com\"/>\n* Berwyn United<ref name=\"ReferenceA\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.danielbiss.com/team-biss-endorsements/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=November 28, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201080830/https://www.danielbiss.com/team-biss-endorsements/ |archive-date=December 1, 2017 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n* BlackRoots Resistance<ref name=\"ReferenceA\"/>\n* Champaign County Young Democrats<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.fac