ald Editorial|last=Board|date=October 12, 2018|website=Daily Herald|accessdate=March 8, 2019}}</ref>\n* ''[[Crain's Chicago Business]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chicagobusiness.com/opinion/jb-pritzker-governor|title=J.B. Pritzker for governor|date=October 4, 2018|website=Crain's Chicago Business|accessdate=March 8, 2019}}</ref>''\n* ''[[Quad-City Times]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://qctimes.com/opinion/editorial/pritzker-offers-way-forward/article_ffca3d35-f0e7-51cb-b478-308a2cb24480.html|title=Pritzker offers way forward|first=Quad-City Times Editorial|last=Board|website=The Quad-City Times|accessdate=March 8, 2019}}</ref>''\n* ''[[Dispatch-Argus]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://qconline.com/opinion/editorial/for-illinois-governor-j-b-pritzker/article_04ea7f9c-5c3d-5e18-a980-eb80d20495b1.html|title=For Illinois governor: J.B. Pritzker|website=Dispatch-Argus-QCOnline|accessdate=March 8, 2019}}</ref>''\n* ''[[Southern Illinoisan|The Southern Illinoisan]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thesouthern.com/opinion/editorial/voice-of-the-southern-despite-our-reservations-we-endorse-j/article_5d8ef1d9-2f4c-5996-9956-7cf79ac11260.html|title=Voice of The Southern: Despite our reservations, we endorse J.B. Pritzker for governor|website=The Southern|accessdate=March 8, 2019}}</ref>''\n}}\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Kash Jackson (L)\n| list =\n;U.S. Governors\n* [[Gary Johnson]], former governor of New Mexico, [[Libertarian Party (United States)|Libertarian Party]] candidate for President in 2012 and 2016, and for U.S. Senator from New Mexico in 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/GovGaryJohnson/status/1057007626381254656|title=Kash Jackson is the kind of fresh voice who can shake up a status quo that is clearly not working. He is one of those rare individuals that is willing to say what needs to be said and do what needs to be done - like addressing broken family courts. #RestoreIllinois|first=Gov Gary|last=Johnson|date=October 29, 2018|publisher=[[Twitter]]|accessdate=Ma