aCharts|Dutch Mega Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"nlchart\">{{cite web|title=dutchcharts.nl The Beatles \u2013 ''Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band''|publisher=[[MegaCharts]]|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Sgt.+Peppers+Lonely+Hearts+Club+Band&cat=a|language=Dutch|work=Hung Medien, dutchcharts.nl|accessdate=1 May 2010|format=ASP|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207213344/http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Sgt%2E+Peppers+Lonely+Hearts+Club+Band&cat=a|archive-date=7 December 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|2\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Japanese Albums Chart<ref name=\"Jachart1\">{{cite book|title=Oricon Album Chart Book: Complete Edition 1970\u20132005|publisher=Oricon Entertainment|location=[[Roppongi]], [[Tokyo]]|year=2006|isbn=4-87131-077-9}}</ref>\n|3\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|UK Albums Chart<ref name=\"ukchart\">{{cite web| url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/Beatles| title=The Beatles > Artists > Official Charts| publisher=[[UK Albums Chart]]| accessdate=1 May 2013| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313042939/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/beatles/| archive-date=13 March 2013| url-status=live}}</ref>\n|3\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+2009 reissue\n|-\n!Chart\n!Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[ARIA Charts|Australian Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://australian-charts.com/weekchart.asp?year=2009&date=20090927&cat=a |title=Album Top 50 |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=16 November 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101026185922/http://australian-charts.com/weekchart.asp?year=2009&date=20090927&cat=a |archive-date=26 October 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|16\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Ultratop|Belgian Albums Chart (Wallonia)]]<ref>{{cite web|title= ultratop.be The Beatles \u2013 ''Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band''|url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Sgt.+Peppers+Lonely+Hearts+Club+B